sources.title: This Little Girl Was Born Bad | Full Movie | Mystery Horror | Abbey Grace
sources.description:
*Abbey Grace* - After the death of her mother, Stacey abandons her own life to return home and care for her reclusive, OCD-afflicted brother Ben, who has been confined to their childhood home for over two decades. Upon her arrival, Stacey uncovers a haunting, long-buried secret - the house, once a boarding facility for orphans, conceals an unspeakable evil that the family had naively presumed would remain hidden forever.
2016.  Stars: Debbie Sheridan, Jacob Hobbs, Amber Gallaway
